      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>The cultivator
               <persName ref="#gaundappaMujgonda">Gaundappa Mujgonda</persName>
                declared before the judge (qazi) that trees
               reported stolen from the garden of a merchant were purchased from the brother of the
                  headman (muqaddam) of the nearby village
               <placeName ref="#nagansur">Nagansur</placeName>.
            </p>
         </abstract>

